 Swedish Academy of Sciences\">Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences<\/a> to name Hauptman and <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Jerome_Karle\" title=\"Jerome Karle\">Jerome Karle<\/a> recipients of the 1985 <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Nobel_Prize_in_Chemistry\" title=\"Nobel Prize in Chemistry\">Nobel Prize in Chemistry<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"Herbert A. Hauptman","place_of_birth":"New York City ,  New York ,  U.S.A.","place_of_death":"Buffalo, New York","text":"Herbert A. Hauptman , Chemistry, 1985","year":1985.0}